room_title: Escape room "Chloe" by Alcatraz Escape Games in Salt Lake City
room_description: There’s a house at the end of the street, one where the air goes cold and stale as you walk by. Abandoned and boarded there has never been a reason to enter…until she returned – or, some part of her returned. Presumed dead, Chloe had been missing for 30 years and now she’s home and want’s to play. Do you dare enter the most terrifying room yet?
